# Code owners for Rekoll.
#
# When someone opens a PR, GitHub automatically requests a review from the
# owner(s) listed here for the files touched. This documents accountability
# (see DESIGN.md §9 — named, real-identity maintainers) and routes reviews.
#
# NOTE: branch protection is intentionally NOT set to "require review from code
# owners" while this is a solo project — that would block you from merging your
# own PRs (you can't approve yourself). This file still routes review requests.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                       @ryankyleocampo-github

# Load-bearing areas — same owner today, but called out so future co-maintainers
# inherit clear ownership boundaries.
